data.description: Set against the backdrop of treetops and mountain vistas, this Coral Tree Plaza southwest corner residence is a visual treat that will awaken your senses. Unwind, as the oversized balcony becomes your private sky-box, offering uninterrupted panoramic views that create enchanting landscapes within your own home. The kitchen features high-end stainless appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinetry and an eat-at bar accentuated by warm drop lighting.  Your tranquil sanctuary awaits in the primary bedroom. It's a haven of relaxation, enhanced with customized built-ins that bring an added touch of sophistication. The upgraded ensuite bathroom indulges you further with an expansive vanity, giving a boutique hotel feel right at home. A step-in shower featuring a rain shower head is the perfect place to rejuvenate. Accompanied by crown molding, pendant & recessed lighting, two dedicated parking spaces and additional storage space, this residence has been thoughtfully designed with your lifestyle in mind. Just a stone's throw away from the verdant Balboa Park and the vivacious heart of Hillcrest, is truly the epitome of urban living redefined.Positioned as a premier residential destination in Hillcrest, Coral Tree Plaza exemplifies urban sophistication with its impressive array of amenities. The property boasts a crystal-clear swimming pool, a rejuvenating spa, perfectly curated tennis courts, and a contemporary fitness center, catering to those with an active lifestyle. Additional features of Coral Tree Plaza include welcoming guest suites and a generously sized club room. This communal space, accentuated by a vintage-style fireplace, becomes a hub for animated conversations, fostering a warm community spirit. For pet owners, an on-site dog run is a convenient amenity, while ample parking facilitates easy visits for guests. Situated in a prime location, the complex offers unparalleled pedestrian access to the lively village of Hillcrest and the verdant tranquility of Balboa Park. For those seeking the buzz of city life, downtown's vibrant heartbeat is just a brief drive away. Residing at Coral Tree Plaza is more than an address; it's a chance to experience an exceptional lifestyle uniquely blending luxury, comfort, and convenience.  Murphy bed inside closet in 2nd bedroom conveys.   3rd optional bedroom has been opened up and is off the living/dining area.
